snippet.title: Die Young - Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://dieyoung.indiegala.com
Out now on Indiegala, Steam and PS4.
Kidnapped for no clear reason to a dazzling yet mysterious island on the Mediterranean Sea, a young girl has to find a way to escape.

The dash for freedom and survival is about to begin and if you’ve got the nerve to face it, welcome to the island! http://indiegala.com/dieyoung

DISCLAIMER: Die Young’s alpha version is as yet an unfinished product subject to modifications and bugs. If you do not want your gameplay experience affected by possible bugs or other minor issues, please hold on for our Steam release this summer.
